# A3DM Design Reference (SPECTRAL)

Source project: `/Users/davidfarrell/Desktop/CASA RPAS STUFF/CASA RPAS STUFF/project`  
Live reference route: `/store` on A3DM localhost:3000

## Visual Language — Zinc Canvas + Orange Accent

| Token | Value | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `--store-bg` | `#080808` | Page canvas |
| `--store-surface` | `#0f0f10` | Panels, sidebar, topbar |
| `--store-surface-2` | `#161618` | Inner wells, inputs, hover |
| `--store-line` | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Borders |
| `--store-ink-soft` | `rgba(244,244,245,0.62)` | Body text — not white, not blue |
| `--store-ink-mute` | `rgba(244,244,245,0.38)` | Muted labels |
| `--store-accent` | `#F97316` | Active nav, CTAs, tabs, prices |
| `--store-accent-glow` | `rgba(249,115,22,0.12)` | Active nav background |
| `--store-accent-border` | `rgba(249,115,22,0.35)` | Active nav border, eyebrow |

Canvas: `hub-page-canvas` — radial orange glow bottom-left + `--store-bg`.

## SPECTRAL ↔ A3DM Brand Mapping

| SPECTRAL | Rule |
|---|---|
| Purple `#A855F7` | Wordmark, EW/AI indicators only — not primary nav active state |
| Orange `#F97316` | Primary CTA, active sidebar item, tabs (A3DM pattern) |
| Cyan `#06B6D4` | Data/spectrum/science UI only — charts, spectrum rail links |
| SPECTRA Liquid Glass rail | **Do not merge** — align tokens only (`/spectrum`) |

A3DM branding: subtle only — footer "Powered by A3DM", login/about credit.

## Layout

- Sidebar: `w-72` / `xl:w-80`, zinc surface, orange active nav
- Main: scrollable; `hub-page-canvas` on `(main)` layout
- Full-bleed (`/map`): `FullBleedShell` slim top bar; `/spectrum` keeps own rail

## Component Patterns

```tsx
// Hub page wrapper
<HubPageShell eyebrow="…" title="…" subtitle="…" headerAction={…} tabs={…}>

// Surfaces
<StorePanel>           // card
<StorePanel inner>     // nested well
<StoreEyebrow>         // orange pill chip

// Primary button
className="store-btn-primary"  // orange bg, #0a0a0a text, rounded-xl

// Active sidebar
className="nav-item-active"
```

